##Types of Operator in Python##
1)Arithmetic Operators
2)Comparison Operators
3)Assignment Operators
4)Logical Operators
5)Bitwise Operators
6)Membership Operators
7)Identity Operators

a**b
--gives a to the power of b

a%b
-- gives remainder

Assignment Operators

c+=a
c-=a
c%=a
c//=a

##Bitwise Operators
1.a&b
2.bin(a&b)
3.a|b
4.bin(a|b)
a = 12
b = 14
a & b
bin(a)
bin(b)
a & b
bin(a&b)
a|b
bin(a|b)
a^b
bin(a^b)

#Membership Operators
a = "I live in India"
india in a

